name: VIRALFACES.002 [selfportraitasadrownedman]
description: The 'VIRALFACES' series started along with my experiences with modular visual programming. The result seems to resonate a lot with the sad and revolting moment that we are living, despite not being the initial intention. I really believe that I discover meanings during the processes way more often than my presumptuous intentions are able to materialize. Image processed via TouchDesigner.
